Package: MeatColor
Title: Meat color analysis from Hunter MiniScan or other colorimeters
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Reese", "Wilson", , "Roofrog764@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to summarize and visualize L*a*b* colorimeter 
    data commonly used in meat science research. The package simplifies the 
    process of creating color visualization plots from colorimeter measurements.
